The annual Capitol Fourth celebrations are a moment for the country to come together and put aside political differences to celebrate our nation's independence. It troubles me the president would attempt to use this event for his own self-aggrandizement https://www.nytimes.com/2019/07/03/us/politics/trump-military-tanks.html …

Today is a chance for our nation to come together & celebrate what we share: a sense of hope and love for the country we call home. Take a moment to reflect upon the ideals & dreams set forth in our founding. Such reflections are important to reaffirm our commitment to democracy. pic.twitter.com/1QL6oObRO6
